Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.85,0:01:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣观音的手所指之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.38,0:01:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将前往\N大富士的山麓之道打开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.69,0:01:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那条路非常险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.72,0:01:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通往地狱深渊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.13,0:02:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第八十六话\N地底的红色蒸气  杀鬼！真田三人众！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.28,0:02:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱深渊吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.31,0:02:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一句显得有点平凡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.62,0:02:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用废话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.05,0:02:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.17,0:02:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像神话中出现的神殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.21,0:02:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是东方人的猴戏罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 修奈特少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.29,0:03:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是钟乳石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.32,0:03:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是漫长岁月当中\N贴下木造的表面的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.83,0:03:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是木造\N怎么看都不像是日本建筑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是\N御沙S祖先制造的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照我们的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.14,0:03:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远在兴盛强大的\N大和势力融合之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.11,0:03:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古代诹访有独自繁荣的文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是真田的祖先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 猴子智慧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.65,0:03:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟想拿祖先\N留下的灵药得到日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.85,0:03:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这只小猴子还挺有智慧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.32,0:03:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若爱惜生命\N就把这只肮脏的手拿开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.49,0:03:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御沙S 这些人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.70,0:03:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,担任我的贴身护卫\N的真田三人众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.64,0:03:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来试试他们有多大本领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.41,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷兹少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.61,0:04:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是来这里战斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你没露出这无礼态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也不会出手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.09,0:04:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说无礼！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.59,0:04:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骑士的座右铭是\N勇气、礼节、名誉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.69,0:04:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对女性的礼节\N应该没有德国日本之分的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.43,0:04:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.23,0:04:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.77,0:04:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照我们的习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.27,0:04:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该对女性表示敬意\N请她先走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 女士优先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.44,0:04:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.56,0:04:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小操 阿薰 你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,头好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有这味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.43,0:04:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们到底怎样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.30,0:05:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 可是照这样下去\N可能会步上前人的后尘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.14,0:05:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前人？这么说这下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别在这地方变成鬼出现\N拜托啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.99,0:05:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到黑骑士团\N会跟真田忍者群联手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.92,0:05:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少罗唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.99,0:05:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又没拜托你过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.33,0:05:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.10,0:05:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你不做好调查\N就进来事情才变成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.73,0:05:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.33,0:05:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个西洋鬼子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.04,0:05:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是石头脑袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.84,0:05:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 石头脑袋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.91,0:05:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看看自己\N是坐在谁的身上打架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.18,0:05:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 这时候还打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之平安无事就太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后要怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.99,0:05:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总不能眼睁睁\N让他们得到宝物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快离开这里吧 好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个臭味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里一片漆黑怎么寻找出口呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.70,0:06:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们以为\N自己跟谁在一起呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看 忍者有这点东西\N是小常识啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.91,0:06:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我马上点火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是御庭番众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.45,0:06:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太可靠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是硫磺的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 如剑心所说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地上有尸体的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.29,0:06:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硫磺与磷份混合起来\N等于是天然的火柴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里点火会大爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.63,0:06:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点程度对人体健康应该没有大碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.67,0:06:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.64,0:06:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 火山活动频繁的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.68,0:06:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会大量喷出瓦斯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间听你慢慢分析了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.95,0:06:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去不需多久\N大家都上西天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 快想办法呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.29,0:06:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对学问没研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好强烈的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 没路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.03,0:07:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无处可退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.67,0:07:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想在这地方变成死人骨头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助 快想办法呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然平日你吃那么多饭\N是干嘛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.38,0:07:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没资格说我我要是有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.49,0:07:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就做了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.16,0:07:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.47,0:07:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.04,0:07:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总算避免窒息而死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地下水脉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个墙壁的另一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.25,0:07:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有地下水流经的水路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要顺水流而走\N说不定可以出去外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.72,0:08:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管三七二十一了\N左之助 该你上场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.36,0:08:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 只要打破墙壁就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.85,0:08:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.01,0:08:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次进来\N不可能知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.09,0:08:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.93,0:08:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.86,0:08:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.93,0:08:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有微妙差别\N但是真的太像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.54,0:08:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真田忍者群传下来的徽章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.27,0:08:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了我们以外应该没人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是凑巧偶然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.21,0:09:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修奈特 除了徽章以外\N没别的线索吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.22,0:09:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.12,0:09:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的被磨灭了看不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.42,0:09:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刻在这上面的文字\N也很酷似西方的古代文字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.93,0:09:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔达斯中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.23,0:09:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边也有同样的东西\N这是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.13,0:09:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来都是置在分歧点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是祖先留下来的路标吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.81,0:09:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.78,0:09:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 看到这个\N我不禁想起我族流传的神话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.65,0:09:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说我们的祖先之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.55,0:09:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一支\N成为海上之民向东渡海而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.29,0:09:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定御沙S你们的祖先…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.19,0:09:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们祖先\N在很久以前是有关联的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.57,0:09:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你是在想这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常有人这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧 天就快要亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.94,0:10:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝到水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看大家这是什么样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.69,0:10:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们下来的方式\N就不能好看一点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.13,0:10:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没那个闲暇呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.13,0:10:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候\N我们还是输给学过忍术的人啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 有个人倒在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.24,0:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方会有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.14,0:10:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家全把我给忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边 由太郎正在照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.45,0:10:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真田的忍者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是伤势很重\N这样下去的话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.63,0:11:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 你还不可以动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.43,0:11:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你受重伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.47,0:11:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.90,0:11:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹也是忍者\N不会轻易死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.21,0:11:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.04,0:11:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.11,0:11:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得非常不解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.25,0:11:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里应该是\N真田忍者群的根据地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是被谁杀伤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.42,0:11:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没必要告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.49,0:11:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不打过来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你们拖下去垫我的棺材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.29,0:11:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事\N难得捡回一条命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没必要浪费它呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不攻过来我就攻过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又昏过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.67,0:11:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.48,0:11:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必需立刻动手术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.74,0:11:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手术？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.95,0:11:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要试试看请大家协助我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.18,0:11:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.15,0:11:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了我能帮多少就帮多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是全部的道具了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞镖可以当手术使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有针跟线 这就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水煮沸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.26,0:12:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻找岩石凹进去的地方\N把汤倒进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.61,0:12:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别摇 要是泼到怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎你想做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消毒呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.18,0:12:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能在不卫生的状态下\N碰触他的伤口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 那是热水耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.65,0:12:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会被烫伤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 快把手拿出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.66,0:12:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.86,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你闭嘴 这是为了拯救患者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.06,0:12:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,患者他是敌人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.70,0:12:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对医生而言 他是病人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.17,0:12:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在医学面前\N没有敌人与自己人之分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.64,0:12:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽力拯救受伤与生病的人\N这就是医生的战斗呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能得救吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.31,0:13:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤口缝好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.14,0:13:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是模仿博士罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.18,0:13:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在\N我是衷心希望他可以救活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎 你很了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.32,0:13:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道西医的伟大之处了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.45,0:13:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家 好了 出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得再次回去那里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.79,0:13:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能把\N神圣的灵药交给他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.23,0:13:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是可能来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做手术时我了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.97,0:13:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神圣的灵药\N是医学发展时所需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.87,0:13:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决不能成为\N他们达成野心的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 你还不能动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫由太郎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.55,0:14:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带我去 我知道秘道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.15,0:14:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.36,0:14:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真田的戒太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.46,0:14:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不会再被准许\N使用真田这名字了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们别被骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可能是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.07,0:14:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假装被自己人背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.03,0:14:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来背后捅我们一刀\N我可受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我了解你怀疑的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.97,0:14:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在事态刻不容缓\N所以还是带我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.25,0:14:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走这条路 可以直接到达\N你们摔下来的那地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.96,0:14:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.82,0:14:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 放心吧 我只是晃了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.46,0:14:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.63,0:14:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的可以信任那男人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在担心 可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.77,0:15:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何不姑且相信戒太看看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.44,0:15:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.14,0:15:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他当烂好人的习惯\N又不是现在才养成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.95,0:15:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.66,0:15:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 从这里直接下去呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.20,0:15:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以赶上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.33,0:15:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先走 一次一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要尽量安静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边也有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 红色头发的剑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.79,0:15:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炼、斩 你们跟漠一起去迎击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.66,0:16:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御沙S 这些蝙蝠是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.57,0:16:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍者的使魔是不限于人类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.81,0:16:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.41,0:16:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿动物当仆人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.04,0:16:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然适合野蛮的东洋猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.58,0:16:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.75,0:16:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些蝙蝠干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漠的蝙蝠脾气很坏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.85,0:16:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激怒他们会讨皮肉痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.22,0:16:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.02,0:16:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了 你们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.90,0:16:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说的话我取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.04,0:16:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们看起来挺可爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.04,0:16:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.04,0:16:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些蝙蝠是头一次\N亲近我跟漠以外的人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.08,0:16:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 我也可以当忍者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.38,0:16:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不知道了\N忍者的修行很严苛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就请你手下留情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.85,0:16:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御沙S
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.79,0:17:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才听你提到\N红色头发的剑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.59,0:17:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.70,0:17:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且带路的人是戒太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.10,0:17:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 戒太是我杀死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.47,0:17:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么\N他们俩都还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.91,0:17:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且使用我们的秘道\N来到附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来他们还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个红色头发的武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.72,0:17:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个小喽喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.32,0:17:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 让我来助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.09,0:17:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 这地方地面不平\N你的竹刀剑术没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方是忍者耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.43,0:17:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是左之助之前不是说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.34,0:17:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎用医术救人\N你就以剑来救人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你该分清楚时机跟场合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.74,0:17:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.24,0:17:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦他是被由太郎的行为\N打动心灵了呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.35,0:18:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦 虽然有点危险\N你愿接下这工作吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在看哪里 这边啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.83,0:18:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.23,0:18:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是小鬼\N我是神谷活心流的明神弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 我当你们对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.57,0:18:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你再也不敢说大话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.95,0:18:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.85,0:18:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.69,0:18:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以站起来吧\N你演得很好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.46,0:18:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少喽唆 不用绕弯来嘲笑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.30,0:18:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有嘲笑你\N刚才真的很神气哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.04,0:18:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.32,0:19:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么西洋的街道会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.66,0:19:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是博士所说的遗迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.77,0:19:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.54,0:19:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.61,0:19:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪个笨蛋\N玩弄这种危险玩具的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又出现一个疯子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.12,0:19:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有猎物了\N我们就玩到过瘾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助 别大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.26,0:19:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.00,0:19:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.06,0:19:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.93,0:19:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是真田三人众的两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个是猎头者“斩”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.27,0:20:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及大蛇“炼”\N不是你能对付的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.01,0:20:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别看不起人了 我可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.05,0:20:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 这些蝙蝠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.25,0:20:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是躲在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.75,0:20:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真田三人众最后一人\N暗使者“漠”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.79,0:20:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去 真是祸不单行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想跟那武士交手一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.00,0:20:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是幕末时期\N被称为传说中的斩人剑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.81,0:20:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村拔刀斋\N这就是他的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.61,0:20:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村拔刀斋\N传说中的斩人剑客吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.08,0:20:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我越来越想跟他交手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.48,0:20:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 那是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.79,0:20:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真田三人众\N大概已经杀死他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.32,0:20:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修奈特\N你在做什么 还不快来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.90,0:20:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.23,0:21:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.93,0:21:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对他不会这么有兴趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 这些是吸血蝙蝠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.95,0:21:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别伤害少女的皮肤啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.92,0:21:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很痛的耶 呆子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.66,0:21:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.50,0:21:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你闪边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.24,0:21:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.94,0:21:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于抓到了
